I22``(2) release public versions of the reports required under section 610(a) and (b).

I21``(c) T4Public HearingsK._Any public hearings of the Commission shall be conducted in a manner consistent with the protection of information provided to or developed for or by the Commission as required by any applicable statute, regulation, or Executive order.

