I11Except as otherwise expressly provided by law, all research and development carried out by or through the Office shall be carried out on a competitive basis.

I19(d) Information from Federal agencies

I11Federal agencies shall, upon request from the Office and in accordance with Federal law, provide the Office with any data, reports, or other information requested, unless compliance with such request is otherwise prohibited by law.

