I11The Office may transfer funds to other Federal agencies or provide funding to non-Federal entities through grants, cooperative agreements, or contracts to carry out its duties under this section: T3ProvidedK, That any such transfer or provision of funding shall be carried out in accordance with section 605 of Public Law 107ÿ0977.

