I89. Definitions

I11In this part:

I79(1) Ammonium nitrate

I12The term ``ammonium nitrate'' means_

I13(A) solid ammonium nitrate that is chiefly the ammonium salt of nitric acid and contains not less than 33 percent nitrogen by weight; and

I13(B) any mixture containing a percentage of ammonium nitrate that is equal to or greater than the percentage determined by the Secretary under section 488a(b) of this title.

I79(2) Ammonium nitrate facility

I12The term ``ammonium nitrate facility'' means any entity that produces, sells or otherwise transfers ownership of, or provides application services for ammonium nitrate.

I79(3) Ammonium nitrate purchaser

I12The term ``ammonium nitrate purchaser'' means any person who purchases ammonium nitrate from an ammonium nitrate facility.

